{
  "page": "Little Rhoyne",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Free_Cities.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Little Rhoyne is located in Free Cities\"><img alt=\"Little Rhoyne is located in Free Cities\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Free_Cities.png/300px-Free_Cities.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"417\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Free_Cities.png/450px-Free_Cities.png 1.5x, /images/a/a3/Free_Cities.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 38.9%; left: 36.9%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Little Rhoyne\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Little Rhoyne</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">Western <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> and the location of the Little Rhoyne\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>The <b>Little Rhoyne</b> is a river in western <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>. Its headwaters lie in the <a href=\"/index.php/Velvet_Hills\" title=\"Velvet Hills\">Velvet Hills</a>, and it is one of the tributaries of the river <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoyne\" title=\"Rhoyne\">Rhoyne</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Ghoyan_Drohe\" title=\"Ghoyan Drohe\">Ghoyan Drohe</a> lies along its banks.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_free_cities.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafthe_free_cities.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The Little Rhoyne is smaller and slower than each of the three forks of the <a href=\"/index.php/Trident\" title=\"Trident\">Trident</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Little_Rhoyne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Little_Rhoyne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> meets the crew of the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Shy_Maid\" title=\"Shy Maid\">Shy Maid</a></i> at <a href=\"/index.php/Ghoyan_Drohe\" title=\"Ghoyan Drohe\">Ghoyan Drohe</a>, and they sail on to the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoyne\" title=\"Rhoyne\">Rhoyne</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Little_Rhoyne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafthe_free_cities.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_free_cities.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>, The Free Cities.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Map_of_the_Free_Cities_(A_Dance_with_Dragons)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Map of the Free Cities (A Dance with Dragons)\">Map of the Free Cities</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_8\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 8\">Chapter 8</a>, Tyrion III.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403120855\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.027 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.028 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 823/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12362/1000000\nPost‐ex